Example config file:
```
# MongoDB Configuration
MONGO_HOST = '127.0.0.1'
MONGO_PORT = 27017
MONGO_DB_NAME = 'dome'

# ZeroMQ Configuration
ZMQ_HOST = '192.168.0.101'
ZMQ_PORT = '5554'
ZMQ_TOPICS = ["task1_events", "task2_images", "task3_windparams"]

# Client folder name
folder_path = ['./input_folder', './input_folder_2', './input_folder_3']

SCAN_INTERVAL_SEC = 10
RETRY_INTERVAL_SEC = 20

```